{"type": "article", "id": 52355, "title": "“无畏女孩”搬家，汉堡王拍了个异装广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-04-20T03:03:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 47871, "name": "无畏女孩"}, {"id": 1628, "name": "汉堡王"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180420104931RN2jcdmGY0InokKX.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44151\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基 X 蜷川实花主题店</b></a>，蜷川实花为肯德基设计了冰淇淋包装，并推出联名限量杯的咖啡饮品，地址位于上海人民广场曼可顿门店。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420103933cNmvijJCBOyzAGH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560870\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420104003AcWZXEfoIwGn6aP8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://creativity-online.com/work/hammer-museumuniqlosolange-metatronia/54326\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优衣库和表演艺术家 Solange（碧昂斯的妹妹）合作</b></a>，让一群舞者在自然环境中的大型白色立方体结构内表演，所有人都穿着一样的颜色，有一种神秘感，同时体现品牌实用简约的审美主张。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420104603qNYrm0hidl56S7oO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font: 16.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #383c40; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 12.0px 'Songti SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #3e3e3e; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #3e3e3e} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/agencies/fearless-girl-will-relocate-to-a-prime-location-facing-the-new-york-stock-exchange/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“无畏女孩”被搬到纽约证券交易所旁边的黄金地段，铜牛的迁移也在计划中。</b></a>这座雕塑由道富环球投资公司（State Street Global Advisors）委托艺术家克里斯汀·维巴斯创作，宣扬女性领导力量，呼吁性别平等。去年春天被放置在华尔街著名铜牛雕塑对面，吸引大量游客前来观看，纽约市政府出于通行安全考虑对其进行了迁移。</p><p>纽交所也在大楼外挂上横幅欢迎“无畏女孩”的加入。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420085508KhmbJrWgD57azpt1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909910\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26774.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>冈本平面广告</b></a>，以桌面为创作背景，设计了主妇的厨房、强迫症的秩序、职员室的短剧等四组场景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420095755Fug3vdSwxiNK6AUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420095820DX3dnUZjVKyhCRxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420095832IYdrOPL9yC02z3Sv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180420095842eUJncRmQT7Mi1dvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/04/13/ad-the-day-one-man-goes-ridiculous-lengths-share-burger-king-with-his-daughter\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>汉堡王北美广告</b></a>，拍摄了一个父亲打扮成小女孩的样子去上学、应付考试，原因是妻子说只有女儿取得好成绩才能吃汉堡王，属于活不过第二集的丈夫吧。短片由 Vincent Lobelle 指导，主打 8-12 岁的青少年市场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z0631mkwf6t&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26775.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">宜家英国的织物广告</a></b>，展现主人不在家“可能”会发生的事。比如说纺织物们办一场狂欢派对。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k0632p8r3kl&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/04/13/ad-the-day-one-man-goes-ridiculous-lengths-share-burger-king-with-his-daughter\" rel=\"nofollow\">thedrum</a></p>"}